message.body: Hey man, Greg here. You still play at dobra with Awar? I'm gonna be in Burlington tomorrow and Wed, are you guys playing? It'd be fun to play a few tunes with you.
I just moved to Philly so I wont be there, everyone else will be tho. Sorry I'm gonna miss you. I hope all is well
Cool man, congratulations. Glad you made it there. I'm sure you'll find many opportunities there.
